taiaha
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a long wooden weapon, pointed at one end, used for striking and jabbing; a Maori quarterstaff
Origin: Maori
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
